# Typography: Heading (Outfit) and Body (Switzer) typescale

Base size: **16px = 1rem**. Set `font-size: 16px` on `html` so all rem values resolve correctly.

## 1. Embed in `<head>` (required)

**Outfit (headings):** In the HTML `<head>` (or in a CSS file loaded by the root HTML), include:

```html
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@100..900&display=swap');
</style>
```

Outfit utility class for headings (weight 600): e.g. `.outfit-heading { font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-weight: 600; font-style: normal; }`. Use a descriptive class name; weight can be 100–900 as needed.

**Switzer (body):** In `<head>`, link the project’s Switzer CSS (e.g. `<link rel="stylesheet" href="path/to/switzer.css">`) or embed its `@font-face` rules. Ensure font files (woff2/woff/ttf) live at the paths referenced in that CSS. Set default body to `font-family: 'Switzer-Variable', 'Switzer-Regular', sans-serif;` (variable covers 100–900).

## 2. Heading typescale

Use **Outfit**, font-weight **600**, and these values for all headings. Map H7–H12 to classes (e.g. `.h7`–`.h12`) where semantic `h1`–`h6` are insufficient.

| Heading | font-size | line-height | letter-spacing |
| ------- | --------- | ------------ | -------------- |
| h1 | 4.5rem | 0.8 | -0.01em |
| h2 | 4rem | 0.7 | -0.01em |
| h3 | 3.5rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| h4 | 3rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| h5 | 2.625rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| h6 | 2.5rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .h7 | 2.25rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .h8 | 2rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .h9 | 1.875rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .h10 | 1.75rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .h11 | 1.5rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .h12 | 1.25rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |

All headings: `font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;`

## 3. Body typescale

Use **Switzer** for body text. Each tier supports font-weight **400** (Regular), **500** (Medium), **600** (Semibold), **700** (Bold). Apply via classes `.body-xl`, `.body-lg`, `.body-md`, `.body-sm`, `.body-xs`, `.body-xx` with the appropriate `font-weight`.

| Class | font-size | line-height | letter-spacing |
| ----- | --------- | ----------- | -------------- |
| .body-xl | 1.25rem | 1.3 | -0.017em |
| .body-lg | 1.125rem | 1.3 | -0.02em |
| .body-md | 1rem | 1.3 | -0.02em |
| .body-sm | 0.875rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .body-xs | 0.75rem | 1.3 | -0.01em |
| .body-xx | 0.625rem | 1.3 | -0.02em |

All body: `font-family: 'Switzer-Variable', 'Switzer-Regular', sans-serif;`

